---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="页面未找到">
  <main class="min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 text-center">
    <div class="relative mb-8 group">
      <h1 class="text-[12rem] md:text-[18rem] font-black italic leading-none tracking-tighter text-nike-grey select-none font-nike transition-all duration-700 group-hover:tracking-widest opacity-20">
        404
      </h1>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center translate-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 animate-pulse">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(239,68,68,0.5)]"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-500">连接中断</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black italic uppercase tracking-tighter text-nike-black font-nike glitch-text" data-text="在赛场外掉线了">
          在赛场外掉线了
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="text-nike-dark-grey text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed">
          哎呀！看来你的连接在关键时刻“掉线”了。<br/>
          主裁判判定该页面因技术违规已离场。
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center pt-4">
        <a href="/" class="btn-nike-black px-12 py-4 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-bold group flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <span>重新热身 (回首页)</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Decorative Elements */}
    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 opacity-40 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
      <div class="text-left space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-nike-dark-grey">热门分类</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm font-bold uppercase space-y-1">
          <li><a href="/topic/men" class="hover:underline">男子</a></li>
          <li><a href="/topic/women" class="hover:underline">女子</a></li>
          <li><a href="/topic/kids" class="hover:underline">儿童</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="text-left space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-nike-dark-grey">精选系列</h3>
        <ul class="text-sm font-bold uppercase space-y-1">
          <li><a href="/topic/jordan" class="hover:underline">Jordan</a></li>
          <li><a href="/topic/running" class="hover:underline">跑步</a></li>
          <li><a href="/topic/basketball" class="hover:underline">篮球</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";

  h1 {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px #e5e5e5;
    text-shadow: 4px 4px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
  }

  .glitch-text {
    position: relative;
    text-shadow: 0.05em 0 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
      -0.025em -0.05em 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
      0.025em 0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    animation: glitch 500ms infinite;
  }

  @keyframes glitch {
    0% {
      text-shadow: 0.05em 0 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        -0.05em -0.025em 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        -0.025em 0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
    14% {
      text-shadow: 0.05em 0 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        -0.05em -0.025em 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        -0.025em 0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
    15% {
      text-shadow: -0.05em -0.025em 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        0.025em 0.025em 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        -0.05em -0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
    49% {
      text-shadow: -0.05em -0.025em 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        0.025em 0.025em 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        -0.05em -0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
    50% {
      text-shadow: 0.025em 0.05em 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        0.05em 0 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        0 -0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
    99% {
      text-shadow: 0.025em 0.05em 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        0.05em 0 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        0 -0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
    100% {
      text-shadow: -0.025em 0 0 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.75),
        -0.025em -0.025em 0 rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.75),
        -0.025em -0.05em 0 rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.75);
    }
  }
</style>
